#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn10.9"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn10.9:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 10 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 10 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn10.9:0.2"
msgid "1. Indakavagga "
msgstr "1. With Indaka "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn10.9:0.3"
msgid "9. Paṭhamasukkāsutta "
msgstr "9. With the Nun Sukkā (1st) "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "sn10.9:1.1"
msgid "Ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā rājagahe viharati veḷuvane kalandakanivāpe. "
msgstr "At one time the Buddha was staying near Rājagaha, in the Bamboo Grove, the squirrels’ feeding ground. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn10.9:1.2"
msgid "Tena kho pana samayena sukkā bhikkhunī mahatiyā parisāya parivutā dhammaṃ deseti. "
msgstr "Now, at that time the nun Sukkā was teaching Dhamma, surrounded by a large assembly. "

msgctxt "sn10.9:1.3"
msgid "Atha kho sukkāya bhikkhuniyā abhippasanno yakkho rājagahe rathikāya rathikaṃ siṅghāṭakena siṅghāṭakaṃ upasaṅkamitvā tāyaṃ velāyaṃ imā gāthāyo abhāsi: "
msgstr "Then a native spirit was so devoted to Sukkā that he went street to street and square to square, and on that occasion recited these verses: "

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. REF: pts2ed1.459, sc2, verse-num-sc842
msgctxt "sn10.9:2.1"
msgid "“Kiṃ me katā rājagahe manussā, "
msgstr "“What’s up with these people in Rājagaha? "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn10.9:2.2"
msgid "Madhupītāva seyare; "
msgstr "They sleep like they’ve been drinking mead! "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn10.9:2.3"
msgid "Ye sukkaṃ na payirupāsanti, "
msgstr "They don’t attend on Sukkā "

# NOTE: In most cases, I have translated the slightly different texts here and at Thig 3.6 the same, this line must clearly be different.
#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn10.9:2.4"
msgid "Desentiṃ amataṃ padaṃ. "
msgstr "as she’s teaching the deathless state. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc3, verse-num-sc843
msgctxt "sn10.9:3.1"
msgid "Tañca pana appaṭivānīyaṃ, "
msgstr "But the wise—"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn10.9:3.2"
msgid "Asecanakamojavaṃ; "
msgstr "it’s as if they drink it up, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn10.9:3.3"
msgid "Pivanti maññe sappaññā, "
msgstr "so irresistible, delicious, and nutritious, "

#. HTML: <br>
#. VAR: Valāhakamiva panthagū”ti → valāhakamivaddhagūti (bj, pts2)
msgctxt "sn10.9:3.4"
msgid "Valāhakamiva panthagū”ti. "
msgstr "like travelers enjoying a cool cloud.”"

#. HTML: </p></article></section></body></html>
